ence McNally, Tony-Winning Playwright of Gay Life, Dies at 81]</ref>\n** [[Albert Uderzo]], French comic book artist (b. [[1927]])<ref>[https://www.repubblica.it/robinson/2020/03/24/news/francia_e_morto_uderzo_fu_il_disegnatore_di_asterix-252148365/ Francia, \u00e8 morto Albert Uderzo: fu il disegnatore di Asterix] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n* [[March 25]] \u2013 [[Inna Makarova]], Soviet and Russian actress (b. [[1926]])<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.starhit.ru/novosti/umerla-inna-makarova-206197/|title=\u0423\u043c\u0435\u0440\u043b\u0430 \u0418\u043d\u043d\u0430 \u041c\u0430\u043a\u0430\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430|lang=ru|website=starhit.ru|date=March 25, 2020|accessdate=March 25, 2020}}</ref>\n* [[March 26]] \u2013 [[Michel Hidalgo]], French footballer and manager (b. [[1933]])<ref>[http://www.foot-national.com/foot-l-ancien-selectionneur-de-l-equipe-de-france-michel-hidalgo-est-decede-131666.html L'ancien s\u00e9lectionneur de l'\u00e9quipe de France Michel Hidalgo est d\u00e9c\u00e9d\u00e9] {{in lang|fr}}</ref>\n* [[March 27]] \u2013 [[Hamed Karoui]], 7th [[Prime Minister of Tunisia]] (b. [[1927]])<ref>[https://www.tunisienumerique.com/derniere-minute-deces-de-hamed-karoui-a-92-ans/ Derni\u00e8re minute: D\u00e9c\u00e8s de Hamed Karoui \u00e0 92 ans] {{in lang|fr}}</ref>\n* [[March 29]]\n**[[Philip W. Anderson]], American Nobel physicist (b. [[1923]])<ref>[https://www.jfdaily.com/news/detail?id=230922 20\u4e16\u7eaa\u7269\u7406\u5b66\u5de8\u4eba\u3001\u8bfa\u5956\u5f97\u4e3b\u83f2\u5229\u666e\u5b89\u5fb7\u68ee\u901d\u4e16\uff0c\u4eab\u5e7496\u5c81] {{in lang|zh}}</ref>\n** [[Yuri Bondarev]], Soviet and Russian writer and screenwriter (b. [[1924]])<ref>[https://tass.ru/kultura/8109675 \u0423\u043c\u0435\u0440 \u043f\u0438\u0441\u0430\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c \u042e\u0440\u0438\u0439 \u0411\u043e\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0435\u0432] {{in lang|ru}}</ref>\n** [[Ken Shimura]], Japanese comedian (b. [[1950]])<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/03/30/world/asia/30reut