alist and writer (b. [[1943]])<ref>[https://elpais.com/ccaa/2020/01/13/catalunya/1578912859_512175.html Fallece la prol\u00edfica y comprometida escritora Isabel-Clara Sim\u00f3 a los 76 a\u00f1os] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* [[January 15]]\n** [[Rocky Johnson]], Canadian professional wrestler (b. [[1944]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tmz.com/2020/01/15/the-rock-father-dad-rocky-johnson-soulman-dead-dies-75/|title=Rocky 'Soulman' Johnson, The Rock's Dad and WWE Superstar, Dead at 75|publisher=[[TMZ]]|date=January 15, 2020}}</ref>\n** [[Christopher Tolkien]], British academic and editor (b. [[1924]])<ref>[https://www.varmatin.com/culture/christopher-le-fils-de-jrr-tolkien-sest-eteint-dans-le-var-a-lage-de-95-ans-448318 Christopher, le fils de J.R.R. Tolkien, s'est \u00e9teint dans le Var \u00e0 l'\u00e2ge de 95 ans] {{in lang|fr}}</ref>\n* [[January 16]] \u2013 [[Efra\u00edn S\u00e1nchez]], Colombian footballer and manager (b. [[1926]])<ref>[https://www.pulzo.com/deportes/muere-bogota-93-anos-edad-efrain-caiman-sanchez-PP829757 Muere a los 93 a\u00f1os \u2018el Caim\u00e1n\u2019 S\u00e1nchez, leyenda del arco de la Selecci\u00f3n Colombia] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* [[January 17]]\n** [[Pietro Anastasi]], Italian footballer (b. [[1948]])<ref>[https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Serie-A/17-01-2020/calcio-piange-pietro-anastasi-fu-simbolo-juve-anni-70-360178677653_amp.shtml Il calcio piange Pietro Anastasi: fu un simbolo della Juve negli Anni 70] {{in lang|it}}</ref>\n** [[Derek Fowlds]], English actor (b. [[1937]])<ref>[https://news.sky.com/story/derek-fowlds-heartbeat-and-yes-minister-actor-dies-aged-82-11910634 Derek Fowlds: Heartbeat and Yes Minister actor dies aged 82]</ref>\n* [[January 19]]\n** [[Jimmy Heath]], American jazz saxophonist (b. [[1926]])<ref>[https://www.npr.org/sections/therecord/2020/01/19/535609079/jazz-saxophone-legend-jimmy-heath-has-died Jazz Saxophone Legend Jimmy Heath Has Died]</ref>\n** [[Shin Kyuk-ho]], South Korean businessman (b. [[1921]])<ref>{